  "risk_acknowledgements": [
    "Fork coins and inherited balances have no promised monetary value.",
    "Inherited scripts are controlled by the same private keys as Bitcoin mainnet scripts.",
    "Fork-only marker replay protection makes inherited-input transactions invalid on Bitcoin mainnet but does not make reused private keys independent.",
    "Never reuse a Bitcoin mainnet private key for convenience; an exposed key can lose real mainnet BTC even when fork coins have no value.",
